   <abstract>The recto for this image shows a man Okie Jones smiling and looking into the distance. Recto reads: Okie Jones -WSM- 'Grand Ole Opry and Television Stars' Columbia Recording Artists Personal Managements Dewey Mousson. Verso reads: This is a sample of our new economy photo postcard The perfect answer to the problem of lowering photo-post card prices for the quantity user. See special price list for Economy Photo Post Cards for further details. Do not confuse with our higher priced genuine photo-post cards described on our photographic price list. Quality of this type of card is comparable to photographic illustrations in high quality  magazines. Mulson Studio.</abstract>
